124
00:08:09,118 --> 00:08:10,912
-Kita ada jadual yang ketat hari ni.
-Saya tak tahu.

125
00:08:11,496 --> 00:08:13,790
Dia ambil cuti hari ni.
Saya nampak dia pergi suatu tempat, berpakaian cantik.

126
00:08:14,374 --> 00:08:16,584
Dia kata dia akan jumpa kita di
tempat bbq.

127
00:08:16,668 --> 00:08:18,169
-Dia mesti jumpa perempuan.
-Mestilah.

128
00:08:18,878 --> 00:08:21,256
Saya tahu. Dia dah bujang terlalu lama.

129
00:08:21,339 --> 00:08:23,174
Saya teka 3 bulan, macam biasa.

130
00:08:23,842 --> 00:08:26,719
Dia kacak,

131
00:08:27,220 --> 00:08:29,305
